# API Reference

Ocsight provides programmatic access to OpenCode usage data through its MCP (Model Context Protocol) server. The MCP server exposes tools and resources for analyzing usage patterns, costs, and development insights.

## MCP Server

Ocsight's MCP server provides AI agents with structured access to OpenCode usage analytics.

### Starting the MCP Server

```bash
# Start the MCP server
ocsight mcp

# The server runs on stdin/stdout for MCP protocol communication
```

